We are using Test Driven Development (TDD) to develop this project.
Always follow the global rules in the .codeium/windsurf/global_rules.md file.
Create a Git repository for this project. Then commit the changes after each step.
After each phase, update the project-structure.md file to reflect the changes.
After each phase, update the docs/ directory with the relevant documentation.
After each phase, push the changes to the remote repository.
Read the project-structure.md file to understand the project structure.
Read the document relevant to the phase you are working on in the docs/ directory.